{"about_the_game":"Discover a thrilling world of adventure in Aetheria, that takes you on a journey through diverse races and unique residences. Navigate challenging obstacles as you fight for survival in a world teeming with danger. And embark on quests to piece together the fragments of your forgotten identity.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/SpireHorizonFlight.gif?t=1707962039\" /><br><br>Embark on a relentless pursuit to defeat a wide array of formidable monsters, pushing yourself to the limits in order to ascend to the pinnacle of power and prowess. Through intense battles , continuously develop your skills and experience, forging a path that leads you to unparalleled greatness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/SpireHorizonMonsterBoar.gif?t=1707962039\" /><br><br>In Aetheria, a multitude of diverse monsters inhabit the various regions, each area harboring its own unique and formidable creatures. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/SpireHorizonHammer.gif?t=1707962039\" /><br><br>Unite with friends to confront mighty bosses, combining your strengths and skills in an epic battle. Together, you'll face overwhelming challenges and stand strong against the formidable forces that await. Victory lies within the bonds of friendship and the power of teamwork.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/SpireHorizonWyvern.gif?t=1707962039\" /><br><br>Master rare weapons and dominate in PvP battles, outshining your friends. Develop your skills to reign supreme, seeking exclusive treasures. Rise to the challenge, leaving rivals in awe.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/combat_12.gif?t=1707962039\" /><br><br>Within the realm of Aetheria, acquiring the necessary materials for armor is an indispensable endeavor, as it holds the key to augmenting one's power and advancing development amidst its vast expanse.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/SpireHorizonMining.gif?t=1707962039\" /><br><br>Escape fatigue, delve into Aetheria's realm, embrace comfort, let tranquility overwhelm. Roam, explore, gather experience from foes, hunt rare weapons, where adventure truly flows.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321880/extras/SpireHorizonChilling.gif?t=1707962039\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Monster Collection - Abomination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321880/810cd611903acfbe78fefcc7fd07ec937b34b168.jpg"},{"name":"Monster Collection - Abyssal Golem","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321880/e0a3a7e28a00990f484193edaeb3923c45a45d41.jpg"},{"name":"Monster Collection - Acromantula","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321880/49a24e04c4fb3f65ac33852c13bb1d20d0b81511.jpg"},{"name":"Monster Collection - Arachna","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321880/f883055783649df12ba7dc721b2beb998f46c873.jpg"},{"name":"Monster Collection - Boar","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321880/2462068ae88c7a8a94e7757a905ed504d0fa71bd.jpg"},{"name":"Monster Collection - Boldas","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321880/47f799a0fd23f016e642997cb3640d8a984abd78.jpg"},{"name":"Monster Collection - Chicken","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2321880/2cf2d5656a2e06c4ed936f59d4630475f367b446.jpg"},{"name":"Monster Col